        <li><a href="/image/svg-to-png/">SVG to PNG Converter</a> — Rasterize vector graphics</li>
        <li><a href="/image/image-to-base64/">Image to Base64</a> — Embed small images directly in HTML/CSS</li>
      </ul>
      <h2 class="section-title section-title-sub">Related Guides</h2>
      <ul class="webp-related-grid webp-related-guides">
        <li><a href="/blog/best-image-format-for-web/">Best Image Format for Websites: WebP vs AVIF vs JPG vs PNG</a></li>
        <li><a href="/blog/heic-vs-jpg/">HEIC vs JPG: Complete Comparison</a></li>
        <li><a href="/blog/convert-iphone-photos-to-jpg/">How to Convert iPhone Photos to JPG</a></li>
